<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png"  href="/images/Powerdrip.png">

  <!-- CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />

  <!-- Pure CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/purecss@3.0.0/build/pure-min.css" integrity="sha384-X38yfunGUhNzHpBaEBsWLO+A0HDYOQi8ufWDkZ0k9e0eXz/tH3II7uKZ9msv++Ls" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/purecss@3.0.0/build/grids-responsive-min.css">
  <!-- Fonts -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Protest+Strike&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  
  <%- include ("partials/header") %>

  <main class="about-page">

    <!-- Intro Section -->
    <section class="about-intro">
      <h1>Fuel Your Grind. Power Your Performance.</h1>
      <p>
        Power Drip is built for people who take their fitness, energy and recovery seriously.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        Power Drip is for the ones who show up every day, whether that's in the gym on the field or just trying to stay consistent.
        We're all about giving you the fuel you need to push harder, recover faster, and stay locked in.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <p>
        From protein-packed smoothies to performance powders and energy drinks, every product we offer is designed with one goal in mind: results.
        No shortcuts, no fluff, just solid products that support your grind.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Our Values</h2>

      <div class="values-list">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Real Performance</h3>
          <p>We focus on what actually helps you improve.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Consistency Over Hype</h3>
          <p>Results come from showing up, not shortcuts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Built For Everyone</h3>
          <p>Whether you're just starting or experienced, we got you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to action-->
    <section class="about-cta">
      <h2>Ready to level up your routine?</h2>
      <p>Check out our products and find what works for you.</p>

      <a href="/products" class="cta-button">Explore Products</a>
    </section>
      
  </main>

  <%- include("partials/footer") %>


</body>
</html>